drama.title: Drama
drama.description: Lose yourself in our thrilling crime tales, historical epics, courtroom dramas, and emotional tearjerkers.

300461.title: Quigley Down Under
300461.description: A man hired as a sharpshooter travels to Australia, where he learns his new, high-paying job has a morbid catch that leaves him conflicted.

300464.title: Return To Me
300464.description: In this romantic comedy, tragedy unites Bob and Grace, who have instant chemistry. But there’s more to their relationship than chance.

302326.title: Gang Related
302326.description: Two men face the consequences after they kill a man and pin the murder on an innocent transient.

308307.title: Buried
308307.description: Paul Conroy wakes up buried six feet underground with a lighter, a rapidly dying cell phone, low oxygen and no idea who put him there or why.

310136.title: Hotel Rwanda
310136.description: The true story of a brave hotel manager who risked his and his family’s lives to harbor over 1,000 refugees during the 1994 Rwandan genocide.

310154.title: 12 Angry Men
310154.description: A twelve-person jury becomes increasingly tense with arguments continuing into the night as one juror must convince the other eleven he is right.

312182.title: Jason's Lyric
312182.description: In inner-city Houston, a man from a struggling family finds love and hope with a woman named Lyric. But secrets from the past threaten his future.

312200.title: Uptown Girls
312200.description: When her inheritance is stolen, a rock 'n' roll heiress must take a job as a nanny to an 8-year-old girl who is more of an adult than she is.

358575.title: Mississippi Burning
358575.description: Based on the true story, two FBI agents investigate the disappearance of three Mississippi civil rights activists in 1964.

367706.title: Jailbait
367706.description: She killed her stepfather in self-defense. Now, Anna must fight her dark side and survive the world of girl gangs and predatory guards in juvy.

399691.title: Requiem for a Dream
399691.description: The lives of four people intertwine in this gut-wrenching, hypnotic tale of addiction and the devastation it has on their lives and those around them.

401472.title: Colors
401472.description: A veteran cop and his new partner are called in to assist with the crackdown against mounting gang violence in the slums of East Los Angeles.

438052.title: Centurion
438052.description: Quintus Dias, the sole survivor of a Pictish raid, marches with General Virilus' Ninth Legion, with orders to destroy the Picts and kill their leader.

451668.title: Miss Meadows
451668.description: Miss Meadows is a just a prim school teacher on the outside but inside hides the soul of a vigilante, righting wrongs by whatever means necessary.

461203.title: Instructions Not Included
461203.description: An Acapulco playboy's life turns upside down when a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep, and he has to raise the child on his own.

466704.title: Jamesy Boy
466704.description: The true story of a teen, who goes from a street gang to a maximum security prison, and the convicted murderer who helps him turn his life around.

469586.title: Hard Target
469586.description: The line between the hunted and the hunter becomes blurred when one man finds himself fighting a group that hunts other men for blood sport.

469821.title: Fear
469821.description: A teenage girl’s dream crush on an older man, whom even her family approves of, turns terrifying when he reveals he’s an obsessed, psychopath stalker.

476915.title: Detachment
476915.description: A substitute teacher who shuns emotional connection bonds with a runaway teenager and becomes a role model for apathetic students at a public school.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

496348.title: American Mary
496348.description: A medical student who can't make ends meet in her profession succumbs to a grisly shadow world of off-the-grid surgeries and warped body modification.

497642.title: Fist of Fury
497642.description: Bruce Lee stars in this iconic action film about a student who fights for the honor of the oppressed Chinese people and to avenge his master’s murder

512252.title: We Need to Talk About Kevin
512252.description: In this suspenseful and gripping psychological thriller, a mother contends for years with the increasing malevolence of her first-born child, Kevin.

521585.title: Amber's Story
521585.description: Dramatized version of the real-life kidnapping of Amber Hagerman and how her family’s crusade to protect children created The Amber Alert system.

528621.title: The Craft
528621.description: The new girl at a Catholic school in L.A. meets a group of socially outcast girls who form a coven with powers that soon backfire in frightening ways.

528667.title: When the Bough Breaks
528667.description: The trust between a married couple and the woman carrying their child is torn when the surrogate decides she wants the husband and baby for herself.

535767.title: Mockingbird Don't Sing
535767.description: The true story of one of the worst and most horrific child abuse cases on record, where a little girl was kept locked in a room for over 12 years.

540236.title: Lolita
540236.description: Modern adaptation of the controversial and classic novel about a British professor who marries his landlord out of sexual obsession with her daughter.

543161.title: Apocalypto
543161.description: A Mayan warrior braves the treacherous jungle to fight off attacking members of an opposing tribe in order to save his family.

550864.title: The Passion of the Christ
550864.description: The brutal portrayal of the final hours in the life of Jesus, as he is betrayed by Judas, condemned to death, tortured, and yet performs one last act of grace.

556004.title: Lucy Shimmers' Christmas Miracle
556004.description: The unlikely friendship between a critically ill little girl and a former felon gives both parties a second chance at life just before Christmas.

557523.title: War Room
557523.description: From the outside, the Jordan family seems to have it all together. But inside, their marriage is crumbling, and they must learn to rely on God.

561890.title: Plug Love
561890.description: After a woman ends her unfaithful relationship, she discovers the value of true love in a world that often prioritizes material wealth.

563040.title: Dead Presidents
563040.description: A Vietnam War veteran returns home and is drawn into a life of crime when he pulls off a daring armored car robbery with a group of fellow vets.

571078.title: Obsessed
571078.description: A happily married businessman finds his life in shambles after a woman pursues him relentlessly, putting his wife in a dangerous predicament.

574217.title: Obsesión (Doblado)
574217.description: Simon hereda una casa de campo en Francia a la que viaja con su esposo y sus dos hijos. Su sueño es renovarla, pero a medida que avanza la reconstrucción, cae en un romance prohibido

582022.title: South Central
582022.description: The ‘90s classic about a respected South Central Los Angeles gang member who, once out of prison, tries to keep his son from going down his old path.

589063.title: The Specialist
589063.description: An ex-CIA explosives expert with his own dark past helps a seductive beauty avenge the murder of her parents by a powerful Cuban-American crime boss.

589172.title: Secondhand Lions
589172.description: Set in the 1960s, this is the story of a 14-year-old’s amazing summer with his unusual uncles, as they tell him tales of their younger days.

591015.title: Proud Mary
591015.description: Taraji P. Henson stars as a steely hit woman working for a local Mob family who finds a protective instinct for a little boy while out for a kill.

591420.title: A Perfect Getaway
591420.description: A romantic Hawaiian vacation turns deadly for two pairs of lovers, when a duo of murderers begins targeting tourists who cannot escape the island.

592664.title: The Miracle Season
592664.description: After their star player dies, a bereaved girl and tenacious coach lead their school volleyball team and town to victory, in this moving true story.

593866.title: Baby Boy
593866.description: The classic John Singleton film about a 20-year-old in South Central L.A. who loves like a man but isn’t stepping up in real life as a grown adult.

597948.title: La Francotiradora (Español)
597948.description: Lyudmila, una destacada francotiradora rusa, se encuentra en peligro después de que un alto comandante alemán ordena eliminarla a cualquier precio.

599603.title: Contagion
599603.description: Oscar®-winning filmmaker Steven Soderbergh (Ocean's Eleven films, Traffic) returns to large-scale cinema with this global action thriller that revolves around the threat of a deadly outbreak of a fatal disease and the people determined to keep it at bay. As the fast-moving epidemic grows, the worldwide medical community races to find a cure and control the panic that spreads faster than the virus itself. At the same time, ordinary people struggle to survive in a society coming apart. A stellar international ensemble cast including Academy Award® winners Matt Damon, Gwyneth Paltrow, Kate Winslet, Marion Cotillard and nominees Jude Law and Laurence Fishburne portray the dedicated doctors at the CDC and World Health Organization who rush to contain the outbreak of a new virus. Tracking its source to Hong Kong and searching for a cure, these determined Samaritans do their utmost to limit deaths, civil unrest and the false rumors surrounding the disease in this viral outbreak drama with multiple plot lines in the style of Soderbergh's Oscar®-winning narcotics drama Traffic.

599629.title: Eyes Wide Shut
599629.description: Tom Cruise and Nicole Kidman star as a married couple entangled in an intricate web of jealousy and sexual obsession in Stanley Kubrick's final cinematic offering.  At a Christmas party hosted by wealthy, unconventional Victor Ziegler (Sydney Pollack), provocative advances and innocent flirtations arouse suspicion as high-society physician Dr. William Harford (Cruise) and his sexy wife, Alice (Kidman) watch each other from a distance. Alone later, this seemingly perfect couple confront their intimate sexual fantasies--which don't include each other.  Caught between reality and illusion, jealousy and obsession, William struggles with his inner urges. Will he act on his erotic fantasies or keep them hidden deep inside? Sometimes a man can see more clearly with his Eyes Wide Shut.

600021.title: Striptease
600021.description: For her most daring role ever, Demi Moore bares all in this erotic satire about a single mother who turns to stripping in a Miami nightclub to earn money for a child-custody battle. But her sensual dancing attracts the unwanted attention of a deranged congressman who will stop at nothing--even murder--to possess her.

605418.title: 90 Minutes in Heaven
605418.description: Based on the New York Times bestseller, this is the story of a man who comes back to life after a terrible car crash, trusting in God to survive.

607105.title: American Me
607105.description: Edward James Olmos stars as a powerful Folsom State prisoner who returns to society after running the game behind bars for 18 years.

609342.title: When Love Kills: The Falicia Blakely Story
609342.description: Looking for a better life for her new baby, 16-year-old Falicia is led down a path of violent crime after taking a job as an exotic dancer.

609721.title: The Karate Kid
609721.description: Jaden Smith stars in the 2010 reboot of the iconic franchise, this time as a young arrival in China who learns self-defense from a karate master.

610572.title: Goodfellas
610572.description: Based on a true story, a young man rises up the ranks of a mob family over several years, dabbling in drugs, heists and murders along the way.

612039.title: He Played Me
612039.description: A woman trying to keep her failing marriage together falls for a man she thinks offers love, but who is only out to destroy her piece by piece.

612777.title: The Kitchen
612777.description: Set in 1978 Hell's Kitchen, this is the story of three housewives whose mobster husbands are sent to prison, leaving them to handle business.

617447.title: Pretty Woman
617447.description: Julia Roberts stars as a witty prostitute who charms a serious businessman, as the two unlikely lovers fall for each other over the course of a week.

619654.title: Ip Man (English Dub)
619654.description: Tells the story of the brutality of the 1939 Japanese occupation of China through the eyes of the Wing Chun grandmaster who rose to fight against it.

619656.title: Ip Man 2 (English Dub)
619656.description: When the Wing Chun grandmaster moves to Hong Kong to open a school for the next generation of fighters, he’s forced to take on a corrupt cabal.

620886.title: The Road
620886.description: Following an apocalyptic event, a father and son travel through North America’s dangerous terrain in the hopes of reaching the ocean.

625256.title: First Sunday
625256.description: Two bumbling criminals discover they haven't got a prayer when they attempt to steal from the local church.

629506.title: Car Wash
629506.description: The disco-themed smash about a day in the life of star-studded clients and the workers at the hippest 1970s car wash in Los Angeles County.

637106.title: Unknown
637106.description: A man awakens from a coma after a car wreck to find his wife doesn’t recognize him, his identity has been stolen, and hitmen are trying to kill him.

637929.title: Carlito's Way
637929.description: In 1975 NYC, a rehabilitated ex-con drug dealer determined to stay clean is tempted back into the life by an array of lowlifes and former associates.

639274.title: La Ley Del Monte
639274.description: Una pareja de niños juran amarse toda la vida y graban sus nombres en la penca de un maguey, pero los padres de ella están en contra de su relación.

639782.title: Ninja Assassin
639782.description: After a trained ninja leaves behind his former life, he works with a Europol agent to take down the hired killers who taught him everything he knows.

639974.title: To Wong Foo, Thanks for Everything! Julie Newmar
639974.description: John Leguizamo, Wesley Snipes, and Patrick Swayze are triple threats in this road trip romp about three drag queens who get stranded in a small town.

641484.title: Brown Sugar
641484.description: A record label producer and his longtime best friend come to the discovery that they’re in love almost immediately after one of them gets engaged.

643528.title: Beaches
643528.description: A lifelong friendship between two women, one a demure, privileged socialite, the other a bold, struggling singer, takes unexpected twists and turns.

644877.title: Rio Lobo

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: When his grandson is kidnapped, the feisty head of his estranged family goes home, supposedly to deliver the ransom, but intending to put up a fight.

646042.title: Sparkle
646042.description: Whitney Houston’s final passion project is the remake about a girl group of sisters whose lives are changed forever by the human cost of fame.

650036.title: Dirty Work
650036.description: A young fashion graduate becomes a personal assistant for an over-the-top erotic novelist, starting an affair that gets her drawn into a murder plot.

651086.title: Hancock
651086.description: A sarcastic, hard-living, misunderstood superhero, whose antics caused him to fall out of favor with the public, saves someone who might save him.

651116.title: Radio
651116.description: The true story of a school coach and a developmentally-challenged man, who inspired a football team to become champions and a town to open its heart.

651120.title: The Tourist
651120.description: An American tourist visiting Italy to mend a broken heart is seduced by a beautiful woman, who ensnares him in an international criminal plot.

654016.title: Something New
654016.description: A workaholic accountant living in Los Angeles must decide between a predictable IBM (Ideal Black Man) and her free-spirited white landscaper.

655363.title: We Bought a Zoo
655363.description: A single dad set out to give his family a fresh start by uprooting them to the Southern California country to a home in the middle of a neglected zoo.

657674.title: The Edge
657674.description: A plane crash in the Alaskan wilderness pits two enemies and a billionaire against a blood-thirsty Kodiak bear in a brutal struggle for survival.

660973.title: Perfume De Violetas
660973.description: Dos adolescentes viviendo en la Ciudad de México entablan una profunda amistad hasta que una de ellas es victima de asalto sexual.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

663544.title: Country Strong
663544.description: A fallen country star strives to resurrect her career with help from her songwriter husband and an emerging artist with a rapidly growing fan base.

664924.title: Daylight
664924.description: When an explosion seals off both ends of a commuter tunnel beneath the Hudson River, a former EMS chief risks it all to save the group trapped inside.

665462.title: Apollo 13
665462.description: A routine space flight becomes a desperate battle of survival in this breathtaking and true-story of adventure, courage, and faith.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

676316.title: Chica Perdida: Una Historia De Hollywood (Doblado)
676316.description: Las historias de cuatro mujeres involucradas en la industria del sexo se entrelazan, ofreciendo un vistazo al lado más oscuro de Los Ángeles.

676725.title: Boyhood
676725.description: Richard Linklater's acclaimed hit, filmed over twelve years with the same cast, is a groundbreaking celebration of life, growing up, and parenting.

677388.title: Secret Society
677388.description: A cautionary tale about two flashy women who get more than they bargained for when the men they seduce for money learn their jaw-dropping secret.

681755.title: Pelé: Birth of a Legend

684095.title: The Cobbler

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99

686285.title: Honey 3: Dare to Dance

686287.title: Honey 4: Rise Up and Dance

686449.title: Honey
686449.description: Pulse-pounding music and awesome dance moves ignite this exhilarating story of one dancer’s passion, courage and determination to follow her dreams.

686450.title: Honey 2
686450.description: After a brush with the law, Maria returns to her Bronx roots with nothing but a talent for street dance and a burning ambition to prove herself.

694757.description: An ambitious heroin dealer has his sights set on becoming the East Coast’s most feared drug lord while battling a high-profile court case.

695341.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?
695341.description: Four couples on an annual retreat struggle to save their marriages while each of them battles their own financial, physical and emotional issues.

696718.title: The Girl Who Believes in Miracles
696718.description: Young Sara discovers her prayers have the power to heal but soon learns the cost may be too high. Can her family save her before it’s too late?

696806.title: A Walk to Remember
696806.description: North Carolina teens Landon Carter and Jamie Sullivan are thrown together after one gets into trouble and is sentenced to community service.

698128.title: Running With the Devil
698128.description: A tenacious federal agent traces the supply line of a ring of experienced cocaine dealers, as two cartel envoys hunt for a shipment lost in transit.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

701396.title: Lamborghini: The Man Behind the Legend
701396.description: This thrilling, high-speed biopic reveals Ferruccio Lamborghini’s dream of making the world’s fastest car—and beating rival Enzo Ferrari to it.

702538.title: Por Tu Maldito Amor
702538.description: Al regresar a su pueblo, un ganadero pelea con el actual esposo de su antiguo amor y una machorra y el dueño de una plantación lo ayudan.

702666.title: El Pequeño Soldado (Doblado)
702666.description: Esta película está basada en la historia real de Seryozha Aleshkov, un niño de seis años, el héroe más joven de Rusia en la Segunda Guerra Mundial.

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
702670.description: Un boxeador retirado entra a trabajar en un centro nocturno donde se enamora de una de las bailarinas y tiene que lidiar con varios personajes.

703674.title: Ultimate Betrayal
703674.description: When lies, secrets, and deceit tear apart a close circle of friends, they learn the definition of keeping your friends close and your enemies closer.

703676.title: He Played Me 2
703676.description: In this sequel, Yazmin recovers and looks to move on from the aftermath of her tumultuous affair with Jai that threatened her life.

708254.title: Samson
708254.description: A child born with supernatural strength in 1200 BC grows up to lead his oppressed tribe with great valor against the mighty empire of his day.

710225.title: The Assistant
710225.description: Raven hires a new personal assistant, thinking she's found the perfect fit. But fear sets in when personal organization turns to personal obsession.

711270.title: Chica Perdida (Doblado)
711270.description: Una adolescente, cuya madre está al final de su carrera como acompañante, tiene que encontrar la manera de ganar dinero para mantener a ambos.

712892.title: Hope Floats
712892.description: After learning about her husband's affair, a former beauty queen moves back to her tiny Texas hometown and reunites with an old flame.

712894.title: The Help
712894.description: In 1960s Mississippi, a Southern girl turns her small town on its ear when she interviews African-American maids who have worked for white families.

713119.title: Alarmed
713119.description: When a couple plans a getaway, things go terribly wrong when their son is held hostage in their high tech home and the only way to save him is to kill or be killed.

714940.title: Secret Society 2: Never Enough
714940.description: Celess is back with a newfound hunger and a bestie on the brink of making it big only to learn that the bigger you become, the harder you fall.

717197.title: True to the Game
717197.description: After falling for a young woman, a charismatic drug lord tries to leave his fast-paced and dangerous lifestyle behind to start a new life.

720943.title: Burlesque
720943.description: A small-town singer moves to the city for a chance at fame when she finds a glamorous nightclub packed with dancers and an owner in need of a star.

720990.title: Til Death Do Us Part
720990.description: When her husband becomes abusive, Madison flees by faking her death and changing her identity. But she soon learns there's no escaping this nightmare.

722979.title: Best Friend
722979.description: Trisha and Jamie have been best friends since grade school. Jamie tries to keep Trisha’s new love interest apart, even if it costs someone’s life.

723254.title: Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World
723254.description: A distinguished young captain of the British Navy leads his crew on a mission to take a French vessel with a reputation for sinking British ships.

723256.title: Red Sparrow
723256.description: A Russian intelligence officer tasked with seducing a CIA agent finds her mission and its objective threatened when they both fall for each other.

723828.title: The Best Offer
723828.description: An eccentric and lonely art auctioneer becomes obsessed with a reclusive heiress he can’t see and who’s hired him to value her family’s collection.

724306.title: Devil's Knot
724306.description: The rural Arkansas town of West Memphis makes national headlines when three teenagers are arrested for the brutal murders of three young boys.

724347.title: The Best Man
724347.description: A Chicago author forces his old friend group to confront secrets from the past when he arrives in town for his best friend’s wedding with a new book.

724377.title: Downfall
724377.description: Traudl Junge, the final secretary for Adolf Hitler, tells of the Nazi dictator's final days in his Berlin bunker at the end of World War II.

724735.title: True to the Game 3
724735.description: Gena wakes to find Quadir is her savior and has just 72 hrs to return to Philly to let Bria and Gah Git know her plans, before her happily ever after.

726033.title: Adulterers
726033.description: A man's fury is awakened when he returns home from work early to find his wife cheating on their wedding anniversary.

100000171.title: Bohemian Rhapsody
100000171.description: Celebrates the rock band Queen, their music and their extraordinary frontman in the years leading up to their appearance at 1985's Live Aid concert.

100000302.title: Real Steel
100000302.description: In a near future where human boxers have been replaced by robots, a struggling ex-boxer and his estranged son reunite while training a robot fighter.

100000719.title: Surprise
100000719.description: Convinced his wife is cheating on him with his best friend, a husband goes off the deep end into a conspiracy, only to find himself unprepared for what comes next.

100000798.title: The Secret She Kept
100000798.description: A successful attorney starts behaving erratically during a political campaign, leading her new husband to suspect she's been hiding a mental illness.

100000946.title: Queen of Kings
100000946.description: Tired of the way she is being treated by the drug lords, dancer Alicia decides to rally her girls to take over the Detroit drug game.

100000965.title: A Good Man
100000965.description: Struggling in the aftermath of his wife's affair, a man's attempt at a new relationship begins to spiral out of control when he notices familiar signs.

100001222.title: Rosewood
100001222.description: In this film inspired by true events, a mob attacks the Black residents of Rosewood, Florida after a false accusation incites racist violence.

100001407.title: Flipped
100001407.description: “Somewhere between confusion and absolute terror,” 8th grader Bryce Loski begins to fall hard for the pesky girl who’s pined for him since age seven.

100001409.title: The Big Red One
100001409.description: Deemed one of the most powerful films ever made about World War II, this story follows a squad of sharpshooters trying not to die in the Big Red One.

100001701.title: Diary of a Unicorn: A Lifestyle Story
100001701.description: Frustrated by an absentee boyfriend, Georgia Morris explores life as a unicorn, joining couples as a third partner in their relationship.

100001725.title: Mindcage
100001725.description: Two detectives must strike a deal with a brilliant serial killer on death row who turned his victims into art exhibits when a copycat killer strikes.

100001799.title: The Raid
100001799.description: When the government’s Armed Offenders Squad launches a raid in his backyard, a local Māori cop must decide which side he will protect and serve. Based on true events.

100001991.title: The Bourne Supremacy
100001991.description: Jason Bourne flees his hiding spot with an assassin at his heels, scouring the globe for answers about his forgotten past while dodging CIA agents.

100001992.title: Illegal Tender
100001992.description: When his family's shadowy past comes back to haunt them, a college student learns the dark source of their wealth and fights off their enemies.

100001993.title: Hanna
100001993.description: Raised in isolation by her father to be the perfect assassin, 16-year-old Hanna sets out on a mission to kill a merciless CIA operative.

100002074.title: Race
100002074.description: Legendary athlete Jesse Owens confronts racism at home and abroad in his quest for gold at the contentious 1936 Olympic Games held in Nazi Germany.

100002112.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 1
100002112.description: After waking up from a four-year coma, a former assassin seeks revenge on the team of killers that betrayed her—and that she was once a part of.

100002113.title: Jackie Brown
100002113.description: Female flight attendant Jackie Brown becomes a key figure in a plot between the federal authorities and her street-tough arms dealer boss.

100002154.title: Damaged Goods
100002154.description: Since he was born, life hasn’t been easy for Chosen. Fending for himself, he quickly learns how to survive on the cold streets of Detroit.

100002155.title: A Body to Kill For
100002155.description: Growing up in Philadelphia, China enjoys a life of privilege until a handsome suitor exposes her to a dark side of the city that changes her forever.

100002159.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
100002159.description: The Bride continues her quest for revenge, fighting her way through a host of assassins in pursuit of a final showdown with the man who betrayed her.

100002270.title: Judas and the Black Messiah
100002270.description: FBI informant William O’Neal infiltrates the Illinois Black Panther Party and is tasked with keeping tabs on their charismatic leader, Fred Hampton.

100002271.title: Cry Macho
100002271.description: A washed-up rodeo star is hired to retrieve his ex-boss’s troublesome son from Mexico. He bonds with the teen during their arduous trip to the border.
